'''Rub<U+00E9>n Cano''' (born [[5 February]] [[1951]] at [[San Rafael, Mendoza|San Rafael]] ([[Argentina]]) is a former Argentinian/[[Spain|Spanish]] [[football (soccer)|footballer]]. He played for [[Atl<U+00E9>tico de Madrid]] between 1976 and 1982, winning the [[La Liga]] title in 1977.

He played 12 times for the [[Spain national football team]] and scored 4 goals. He played in the [[1978 FIFA World Cup]] and the [[1980 UEFA European Football Championship]].

